stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OPEN : Cart.create()\n[UC-ORD-001 CreateCart]

    OPEN --> CHECKED_OUT : Cart.checkout()\n[UC-ORD-005 Checkout]

    CHECKED_OUT --> [*] : Terminal state

    note right of OPEN
        ORD-RULE-001: at least one item (checkout guard)
        ORD-RULE-002: must be OPEN to modify items
        ORD-RULE-004: one OPEN cart per customer (create guard)
    end note

    note right of CHECKED_OUT
        ORD-RULE-003: terminal — no modifications allowed
        Order created → OrderPlaced emitted
    end note
